    SELECT TOP(2) [a].[Id], [a].[CategoryId], [a].[CreatedDate], [a].[CreatorId], [a].[EditRoleString], [a].[IsPublic], [a].[Title], [a].[TitleImageId], [a].[UpdatedDate], [a].[ViewRoleString], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[CreatorId] AS [CreatorId0], [c].[Title] AS [Title0], [c].[TitleImageId] AS [TitleImageId0], [c].[UpdatedDate] AS [UpdatedDate0], [m].[Id] AS [Id1], [m].[ArticleId], [m].[Path], [m].[Type], [p].[Id] AS [Id2], [p].[IdentityUserId]
    FROM [Articles] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [a].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [MediaFiles] AS [m] ON [a].[TitleImageId] = [m].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [Profiles] AS [p] ON [a].[CreatorId] = [p].[Id]
    WHERE ([a].[Id] = @__request_Id_0) AND ([a].[ViewRoleString] IN (N'ViewAAA', N'EditAAA', N'ViewA', N'EditA', N'EditFJoid', N'ViewFJoid') OR ([a].[IsPublic] = CAST(1 AS bit)))
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [MediaFiles] AS [m0] ON [t].[Id] = [m0].[ArticleId]
LEFT JOIN [Subarticles] AS [s] ON [t].[Id] = [s].[ArticleId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [m0].[Id], [s].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(2) [a].[Id], [a].[CategoryId], [a].[CreatedDate], [a].[CreatorId], [a].[EditRoleString], [a].[IsPublic], [a].[Title], [a].[TitleImageId], [a].[UpdatedDate], [a].[ViewRoleString], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[CreatorId] AS [CreatorId0], [c].[Title] AS [Title0], [c].[TitleImageId] AS [TitleImageId0], [c].[UpdatedDate] AS [UpdatedDate0], [m].[Id] AS [Id1], [m].[ArticleId], [m].[Path], [m].[Type], [p].[Id] AS [Id2], [p].[IdentityUserId]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[CreatorId], [t].[EditRoleString], [t].[IsPublic], [t].[Title], [t].[TitleImageId], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[ViewRoleString], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[CreatorId0], [t].[Title0], [t].[TitleImageId0], [t].[UpdatedDate0], [t].[Id1], [t].[ArticleId], [t].[Path], [t].[Type], [t].[Id2], [t].[IdentityUserId], [m0].[Id], [m0].[ArticleId], [m0].[Path], [m0].[Type], [s].[Id], [s].[ArticleId], [s].[Content], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Title], [s].[UpdatedDate]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [a].[Id], [a].[CategoryId], [a].[CreatedDate], [a].[CreatorId], [a].[EditRoleString], [a].[IsPublic], [a].[Title], [a].[TitleImageId], [a].[UpdatedDate], [a].[ViewRoleString], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[CreatorId] AS [CreatorId0], [c].[Title] AS [Title0], [c].[TitleImageId] AS [TitleImageId0], [c].[UpdatedDate] AS [UpdatedDate0], [m].[Id] AS [Id1], [m].[ArticleId], [m].[Path], [m].[Type], [p].[Id] AS [Id2], [p].[IdentityUserId]
    FROM [Articles] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [a].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [MediaFiles] AS [m] ON [a].[TitleImageId] = [m].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [Profiles] AS [p] ON [a].[CreatorId] = [p].[Id]
    WHERE ([a].[Id] = @__request_Id_0) AND ([a].[ViewRoleString] IN (N'EditA', N'ViewA') OR ([a].[IsPublic] = CAST(1 AS bit)))
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [MediaFiles] AS [m0] ON [t].[Id] = [m0].[ArticleId]
LEFT JOIN [Subarticles] AS [s] ON [t].[Id] = [s].[ArticleId]
ORDER BY [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [m0].[Id], [s].[Id]

    SELECT TOP(2) [a].[Id], [a].[CategoryId], [a].[CreatedDate], [a].[CreatorId], [a].[EditRoleString], [a].[IsPublic], [a].[Title], [a].[TitleImageId], [a].[UpdatedDate], [a].[ViewRoleString], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[CreatorId] AS [CreatorId0], [c].[Title] AS [Title0], [c].[TitleImageId] AS [TitleImageId0], [c].[UpdatedDate] AS [UpdatedDate0], [m].[Id] AS [Id1], [m].[ArticleId], [m].[Path], [m].[Type], [p].[Id] AS [Id2], [p].[IdentityUserId]

LEFT JOIN [MediaFiles] AS [m] ON [a].[TitleImageId] = [m].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [a].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[AccessType], [a0].[ArticleId], [a0].[ProfileId], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[IdentityUserId]
    FROM [AccessRequests] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [Profiles] AS [p0] ON [a0].[ProfileId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[ArticleId]
WHERE [p].[IdentityUserId] = @__request_IdentityUserId_0
ORDER BY [a].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]

SELECT [t].[Id], [t].[CategoryId], [t].[CreatedDate], [t].[CreatorId], [t].[EditRoleString], [t].[IsPublic], [t].[Title], [t].[TitleImageId], [t].[UpdatedDate], [t].[ViewRoleString], [t].[Id0], [t].[CreatedDate0], [t].[CreatorId0], [t].[Title0], [t].[TitleImageId0], [t].[UpdatedDate0], [t].[Id1], [t].[ArticleId], [t].[Path], [t].[Type], [t].[Id2], [t].[IdentityUserId], [m0].[Id], [m0].[ArticleId], [m0].[Path], [m0].[Type], [s].[Id], [s].[ArticleId], [s].[Content], [s].[CreatedDate], [s].[Title], [s].[UpdatedDate]
FROM (
    SELECT TOP(2) [a].[Id], [a].[CategoryId], [a].[CreatedDate], [a].[CreatorId], [a].[EditRoleString], [a].[IsPublic], [a].[Title], [a].[TitleImageId], [a].[UpdatedDate], [a].[ViewRoleString], [c].[Id] AS [Id0], [c].[CreatedDate] AS [CreatedDate0], [c].[CreatorId] AS [CreatorId0], [c].[Title] AS [Title0], [c].[TitleImageId] AS [TitleImageId0], [c].[UpdatedDate] AS [UpdatedDate0], [m].[Id] AS [Id1], [m].[ArticleId], [m].[Path], [m].[Type], [p].[Id] AS [Id2], [p].[IdentityUserId]
    FROM [Articles] AS [a]
    INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [a].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [MediaFiles] AS [m] ON [a].[TitleImageId] = [m].[Id]
    LEFT JOIN [Profiles] AS [p] ON [a].[CreatorId] = [p].[Id]
    WHERE ([a].[Id] = @__request_Id_0) AND ([a].[ViewRoleString] IN (N'ViewA', N'EditA') OR ([a].[IsPublic] = CAST(1 AS bit)))
) AS [t]
LEFT JOIN [MediaFiles] AS [m0] ON [t].[Id] = [m0].[ArticleId]

SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[CategoryId], [a].[CreatedDate], [a].[CreatorId], [a].[EditRoleString], [a].[IsPublic], [a].[Title], [a].[TitleImageId], [a].[UpdatedDate], [a].[ViewRoleString], [p].[Id], [p].[IdentityUserId], [m].[Id], [m].[ArticleId], [m].[Path], [m].[Type], [c].[Id], [c].[CreatedDate], [c].[CreatorId], [c].[Title], [c].[TitleImageId], [c].[UpdatedDate], [t].[Id], [t].[AccessType], [t].[ArticleId], [t].[ProfileId], [t].[Id0], [t].[IdentityUserId]
FROM [Articles] AS [a]
LEFT JOIN [Profiles] AS [p] ON [a].[CreatorId] = [p].[Id]
LEFT JOIN [MediaFiles] AS [m] ON [a].[TitleImageId] = [m].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [a].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]

    SELECT [a0].[Id], [a0].[AccessType], [a0].[ArticleId], [a0].[ProfileId], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[IdentityUserId]
    FROM [AccessRequests] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [Profiles] AS [p0] ON [a0].[ProfileId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [a].[Id] = [t].[ArticleId]
WHERE [p].[IdentityUserId] = @__request_IdentityUserId_0
ORDER BY [a].[Id], [c].[Id], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0]
